    question: '<p>Which form attribute allows a number to be entered in a specified interval, such as (-5, 0, 5, 10, etc)?</p>\n<pre><code class="language-html">&#x3C;form\n  action="file.php">\n &#x3C;input\n  type="number"\n  name="points"\n  ???="5">\n  &#x3C;input\n  type="submit">\n&#x3C;/form>\n</code></pre>\n',
